timelineItems.text: It's good to see #RBNY flying after the New England match. Shots could be better, but the team is controlling play for the most part.

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: The Timbers are letting Kljestan get on the ball in central spaces way too much. Playing with fire. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Kyle McCarthy
